---
import CalButton from '../../CalButton.astro'
---

<div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-surface to-base py-24 sm:py-32">
  <!-- Ambient light gradients -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute -top-16 left-1/2 h-[360px] w-[560px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-cream/12 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 -left-20 h-[260px] w-[340px] rounded-full bg-sage/18 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <!-- Large ghosted watermark -->
  <div class="font-heading pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-0 select-none leading-none text-wm font-bold text-white/[0.04]"
    aria-hidden='true'>
    REAL
  </div>
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-cream">CONSULTOR SEO BUENO: SIN TESTIMONIOS DE PAGO</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-h2 font-heading font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-cream">Aquí no hay <s class="text-sage decoration-cream">testimonios.</s></p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="h-px w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-cream/5 to-cream/35"></div>
        <div class="h-px w-10 bg-cream/60"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-base text-cream/70 leading-relaxed text-pretty">La mayoría de consultores SEOs te llenan la página de testimonios que no puedes verificar. Personas que probablemente no conoces, no vas a conocer nunca, y cuya página web ni siquiera puedes buscar. Yo te doy algo mejor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 flow-root max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <figure class="relative rounded-2xl bg-base p-8 text-sm/6">
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="font-heading text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-cream/40 border border-cream/30 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5">DUDOSO</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-cream">
              <p>"El mejor de Barcelona. Rápido, claro y con resultados. ¡100% recomendado!"</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80" alt="" class="size-10 rounded-full bg-sage" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-cream">María G.</div>
                <div class="text-cream/60">Tienda online</div>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div>
          <figure class="relative rounded-2xl bg-base p-8 text-sm/6">
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="font-heading text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-cream/40 border border-cream/30 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5">DUDOSO</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-cream">
              <p>"Hace lo que dice y funciona de verdad. En dos meses empezamos a aparecer en Google y las reservas subieron un montón."</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519244703995-f4e0f30006d5?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80" alt="" class="size-10 rounded-full bg-sage" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-cream">Jordi P.</div>
                <div class="text-cream/60">Restaurante</div>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div>
          <figure class="relative rounded-2xl bg-base p-8 text-sm/6">
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="font-heading text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-cream/40 border border-cream/30 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5">DUDOSO</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-cream">
              <p>"Muy profesional y cercano. Nos explicó todo y los resultados llegaron antes de lo esperado."</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80" alt="" class="size-10 rounded-full bg-sage" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-cream">Montse R.</div>
                <div class="text-cream/60">Clínica dental</div>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 rounded-2xl bg-sage px-8 py-7 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="font-heading text-white text-h6 leading-snug">Mándame tu web, gratis.</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-base text-white/90">Te digo exactamente por qué Google no te muestra.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 shrink-0">
        <span class="text-cream/60 text-2xl rotate-[-10deg]">→</span>
          <CalButton variant="cream" class="px-4 py-2.5 whitespace-nowrap" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
